-Let's go elsewhere, okay?
-Yes, sir.

20
00:02:44,664 --> 00:02:46,374
This is tasty. My gosh!

21
00:02:47,083 --> 00:02:49,377
Goodness! I'm so sorry!

22
00:02:49,460 --> 00:02:51,504
-Come on!
-You're all drenched!

23
00:02:51,588 --> 00:02:53,423
